---

## Verification Standard

Every claim requires ALL THREE proof artifacts (AND logic):

| Layer | Proof | Where |
|-------|-------|-------|
| **1. OTEL Span** | Operation execution with service, span_name, status, attributes | Jaeger UI |
| **2. Test Assertion** | TDD Green test with assertion on exact behavior | `*_test.{rs,go,exs}` |
| **3. Weaver Schema** | Span definition in semconv; `weaver registry check` exits 0 | `semconv/model/` |

