## Merge Gate

- [ ] All **critical** checks verified
- [ ] All three proof layers exist for every claim (OTEL + Test + Weaver)
- [ ] Zero compiler warnings (`cargo clippy -- -D warnings`)
- [ ] Zero test failures (`cargo test`)
- [ ] Weaver registry check exits 0
- [ ] Git commit follows conventional format

